These two lines in execute():

    acl.addPathElement(f.getAbsolutePath());
    log("Adding to class loader " +  acl + " " + f.getAbsolutePath(), Project.MSG_DEBUG);

should be reversed.  Currently the path is added, then when the log message is displayed, the toString() of acl spits out the acl's full classpath, which already includes the path.  This makes it look like it is already in there when adding.
